label: DRAW
description: all sorts of drawings, line art, pen or pencil sketches, paintings, maps, diagrams or schematics, potentially annotated with textual object identifiers

label: TEXT
description: plain printed, machine typed, or hand-written text as the only content of the page

label: LINE
description: table or form, cells with clear border or edgeless cells forming clear rows and columns

label: PHOTO
description: full photos or cutouts from photos, any size and form, potentially annotated with text
